<p>
It is true that people work long hours; most of them start at 10am and
don't leave before 22 PM. 
As for lunch, they go buy a bento that is usually eaten in front of the monitor.
The favourite bento is rice with either chicken or pork and
a fried ball called <em>michi</em> that contains all the ingredients of the known universe.
</p>
